### TRELLO CLONE REST API TESTS
### Use this file with the "REST Client" extension in VS Code!

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
# Variables to replace with actual UUIDs generated from your seeds!
@boardId = PASTE_BOARD_UUID_HERE
@listId = PASTE_LIST_UUID_HERE
@cardId = PASTE_CARD_UUID_HERE

### Get All Boards
GET {{baseUrl}}/boards

### Create a Board
POST {{baseUrl}}/boards
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Board Test"
}

### Get Board by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/boards/{{boardId}}

### ----------------------------
### LISTS
### ----------------------------

### Get all Lists for Board
GET {{baseUrl}}/lists?boardId={{boardId}}

### Reorder List
PUT {{baseUrl}}/lists/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "boardId": "{{boardId}}",
  "sourceIndex": 1,
  "destinationIndex": 0
}

### ----------------------------
### CARDS
### ----------------------------

### Search/Filter Cards
GET {{baseUrl}}/cards/search?query=Design&dueDate=2026-10-10T00:00:00.000Z

### Move Card across Lists
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cards/move
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardId": "{{cardId}}",
  "sourceListId": "{{listId}}",
  "destinationListId": "paste-different-list-uuid-here",
  "destinationIndex": 0
}

### ----------------------------
### ASSOCIATIONS (Checklists)
### ----------------------------

### Create Checklist on Card
POST {{baseUrl}}/checklists
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardId": "{{cardId}}"
}
